<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MedRecord — Acceso Denegado</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
        :root{--navy:#0a1628;--teal:#0d9488;--teal-light:#14b8a6;--blue:#1d4ed8;--gray:#94a3b8}
        body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:#f1f5f9;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
        .card{background:white;border-radius:20px;padding:3rem;text-align:center;max-width:480px;width:100%;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
        .icon{width:80px;height:80px;background:#fef2f2;border-radius:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;color:#ef4444}
        .icon svg{width:40px;height:40px}
        h1{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:2rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.5rem}
        p{color:var(--gray);font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:2rem}
        .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.875rem 1.75rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal),var(--blue));color:white;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem}
        .code{font-size:5rem;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="code">403</div>
        <div class="icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 8 12 4.16-1.26 8-6.45 8-12V5l-8-4zm0 4l5 2.18V11c0 3.5-2.33 6.79-5 7.93C9.33 17.79 7 14.5 7 11V7.18L12 5zm-1 3v4h2V8h-2zm0 6v2h2v-2h-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Acceso Denegado</h1>
        <p>No tienes permisos suficientes para acceder a este recurso. Si crees que es un error contacta con el administrador.</p>
        <a href="{{ app.user ? path('app_dashboard') : path('app_login') }}" class="btn">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 11H7.83l5.59-5.59L12 4l-8 8 8 8 1.41-1.41L7.83 13H20v-2z"/></svg>
            Volver al inicio
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
